rs%20and%20a%20former%20PwC%20partner%20for%20their%20tips%20for%20making%20it%20to%20the%20top%20rank.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETheir%20advice%20includes%20developing%20a%20commercial%20mindset%2C%20being%20a%20team%20player%2C%20and%20learning%20to%20navigate%20internal%20politics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20it%20to%20partner%20at%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-ey-staff-revenues-focus-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%3C%2Fa%3E%20professional%20services%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20Deloitte%2C%20EY%2C%20PwC%2C%20and%20KPMG%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20success%20for%20many%20consultants%20and%20accountants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartners%20are%20the%20firms'%20most%20senior%20employees.%20Those%20who%20hold%20equity%20in%20the%20business%20traditionally%20get%20a%20vote%20in%20strategic%20matters%20and%20a%20share%20of%20annual%20profits.%20That%20meant%20each%20of%20Deloitte's%20equity%20partners%20in%20the%20UK%20received%20the%20equivalent%20of%20%241.3%20million%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecoming%20a%20partner%20is%20notoriously%20difficult%2C%20and%20is%20only%20getting%20more%20competitive%20as%20structural%20shake-ups%20and%20slowing%20growth%20have%20reduced%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpwc-uk-partner-departures-big-four-slowdown-consulting-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartner%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpartner-pay-at-big-four-falling-ey-pwc-deloitte-kpmg-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannual%20payouts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20two%20recruiters%20who%20place%20partners%20at%20the%20Big%20Four%20firms%20and%20a%20former%20PwC%20partner%20who%20recently%20left%20the%20firm%20for%20the%20advice%20they'd%20give%20early-career%20employees%20who%20want%20the%20coveted%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-t