the%20firm%20helped%20his%20career.%3Cp%3EEuropa%20Press%20News%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20junior%2C%20you%20should%20start%20putting%20your%20hand%20up%20to%20do%20the%20tasks%20other%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20do%2C%20said%20O'Dowd.%20Over%20your%20career%2C%20that%20will%20build%20you%20a%20reputation%20as%20someone%20who%20can%20get%20stuff%20done%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Webster%20is%20a%20former%20EY%20employee%20who's%20now%20a%20managing%20partner%20at%20Page%20Executive%2C%20a%20senior%20talent%20recruitment%20firm.%20He%20said%20there%20was%20no%20doubt%20that%20networking%20was%20a%20necessary%20skill%20at%20the%20Big%20Four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWebster%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20the%20advisory%20world%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years%2C%20advised%20employees%20to%20start%20incorporating%20more%20networking%20and%20client%20events%20into%20their%20schedules%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bbe%20good%20at%20schmoozing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20also%20draw%20on%20these%20social%20skills%20to%20be%20a%20team%20player%2C%20Webster%20added.%20Whereas%20other%20industries%20have%20more%20of%20a%20focus%20on%20individual%20performance%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Big%20Four%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20you%20trying%20to%20get%20ahead%20by%20stepping%20on%20someone%20else's%20toes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20trying%20to%20help%20the%20team%20win%20so%20that%20the%20firm%20gets%20ahead.%20They%20particularly%20venerate%20collaboration%20and%20an%20extremely%20collegiate%20style.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d3e338d-1430-477f-a2d3-6760f71949ab%5C%22%3EDevelop%20a%20commercial%20mindset%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20a%20partner%20in%20a%20Big%20Four%20is%20a%20sales%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Dowd%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BYour%20sole%20focus%20is%20on%20winning%20and%20nurturing%20client%20relationships.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20Big%20Four%20career%20meant%20transitioning%20from%20doer%20to%20revenue%20generator%20to%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20progress%20through%20those%20levels%2C%20you're%20increasingly%20managing%20people%20and%20then%20eventually%20the%20onus%20is%20on%20not%20only%20managing%20but%20bringing%20in%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20developing%20those%20skills%20from%20an%20early%20point%20will%20help%20to%20set%20you%20apart%2C%20O'Dowd%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20everyday%20tasks%20don't%20require%20commercial%20skills%2C%20he%20advised%20junior%20employees%20to%20get%20as%20much%20exposure%20as%20they%20can%20to%20the%20commercial%20side%20of%20projects%20by%20attending%20client-facing%20meetings%20and%20connecting%20with%20people%20who%20are%20known%20for%20doing%20it%20really%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Dowd%20added%20that%20senior%20partners%20tend%20to%20frown%20on%20those%20who%20work%20from%20home%2C%20preferring%20people%20to%20demonstrate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-remote-work-weird-habits-return-to-office-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20interpersonal%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20necessary%20for%20commercial%20business%2C%20so%20going%20to%20the%20office%20is%20a%20good%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWebster%20said%20the%20focus%20on%20business%20skills%20has%20become%20even%20more%20pertinent%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20you're%20getting%20up%20to%20senior%20manager%20grade%2C%20they%20now%20start%20to%20expect%20you%20to%20have%20some%20level%20of%20a%20Rolodex%20or%20some%20contacts%20or%20some%20sort%20of%20ability%20to%20bring%20in%20business%20even%20before%20you%20get%20to%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7602a76-a24d-440d-b794-89a7844bcaae%5C%22%3EClimbing%20the%20ranks%20isn't%20the%20only%20option%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20your%20way%20up%20the%20ranks%20internally%20isn't%20the%20only%20way%20to%20a%20Big%20Four%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlan%20Paton%20joined%20PwC%20as%20an%20equity%20partner%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-changes-landed-teacher-job-google-big-tech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20worked%20in%20AI%20cloud%20capabilities%20in%20its%20financial%20services%20division%20before%20leaving%20the%20Big%20Four%20firm%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20that%20joining%20the%20firm%20required%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20individual%20interviews%2C%20panel%20interviews%2C%20personality%20and%20academic%20references%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20was%20while%20being%20%26quot%3Bfast-tracked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22PwC%20building%20against%20a%20blue%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6800eba13fe8d39283635004%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPwC%20is%20one%20of%20the%20Big%20Four%20firms.%3Cp%3ENicol%C3%B2%20Campo%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20hiring%20decision%20is%20based%20on%20the%20business%20case%2C%20so%20to%20become%20a%20partner%20from%20an%20external%20company%2C%20you%20have%20to%20have%20specific%20skills%20the%20firm%20is%20lacking%2C%20Paton%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20firms%20are%20desperate%20for%20high-quality%20people%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeloitte-ey-launch-agentic-ai-platforms-big-four-competition2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%2C%20AI%2C%20data%2C%20and%20tech%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20anything%20else%20will%20not%20get%20you%20very%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20tough%26quot%3B%20to%20break%20into%20the%20Big%20Four%20from%20a%20smaller%20consulting%20firm%20if%20your%20work%20cons