3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20response%20was%20that%20nothing%20had%20changed%20for%20me.%20The%20utility%20of%20the%20car%20was%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20some%20research%20afterward%20and%20saw%20that%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-showroom-design-architecture-marketing-perfect-targets-elon-musk-protests-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotests%20at%20Tesla%20dealerships%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-responds-tesla-vandalism-protests-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eviolent%20acts%20around%20Teslas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Regardless%20of%20what%20people's%20political%20views%20are%20about%20my%20vehicle%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20wrong%20that%20people%20are%20vandalizing%20Teslas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20when%20I%20was%20driving%20my%20granddaughter%2C%20someone%20in%20a%20truck%20behind%20me%20drove%20up%20aggressively%20close%20to%20me%20and%20sandwiched%20me%20between%20them%20and%20the%20car%20in%20front.%20They%20started%20beeping%20and%20yelling%20at%20me.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20this%20was%20because%20of%20my%20Tesla%2C%20but%20I%20assumed%20that%20it%20was%20because%20it%20coincided%20with%20media%20reporting%20of%20Tesla%20vandalism%2C%20and%20there%20aren't%20many%20other%20Teslas%20in%20my%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20this%20is%20speculative%2C%20I'm%20now%20wondering%20whether%20my%20vehicle%20choice%20is%20putting%20me%20in%20a%20bad%20position%20safety-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20yet%20feel%20unsafe%20enough%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20my%20Tesla%2C%20but%20it%20saddens%20me%20that%20I%20may%20have%20to%20make%20a%20decision%20about%20changing%20my%20car%20based%20on%20other%20people's%20perceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDriving%20a%20Tesla%20doesn't%20automatically%20mean%20I%20support%20what%20Elon%20is%20doing%20or%20have%20a%20particular%20political%20view.%20I%20don't%20think%20people%20should%20make