E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDoctronic%20just%20raised%20%245%20million%20from%20Union%20Square%20Ventures%20for%20its%20healthcare%20AI%20agents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup's%20AI%20gives%20personalized%20advice%20on%20users'%20health%20questions%20and%20access%20to%20virtual%20doctors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20competing%20in%20a%20hot%20space%20against%20startups%20like%20Roon%20and%20tech%20giants%20like%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDoctronic%20is%20Matt%20Pavelle's%20twelfth%20startup.%20He's%20launched%20and%20led%20companies%20for%20renters'%20rewards%2C%20wine%20shopping%2C%20and%20luxury%20fashion.%20About%20two-thirds%20of%20them%20have%20been%20direct-to-consumer%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20have%20contracted%20with%20businesses%20to%20reach%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoctronic%20brings%20Pavelle's%20longtime%20consumer%20focus%20to%20a%20new%20domain%3A%20healthcare%20AI.%20And%20Doctronic%20has%20raised%20%245%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%2C%20led%20by%20Union%20Square%20Ventures%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20Tusk%20Ventures%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falcohol-free-san-francisco-house-hf0-ai-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20accelerator%20HF0%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%2C%20and%20now%20AI%20models%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-gpt4-rebuild-breakthroughs-sam-altman-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20receive%20hundreds%20of%20millions%2C%20if%20not%20billions%2C%20of%20health-related%20questions%20from%20their%20users%20every%20day.%20Doctronic%20wants%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20improve%20that%20system%20by%20connecting%20patients%20with%20AI%20agents%20that%20can%20provide%20them%20with%20fast%2C%20anonymous%2C%20and%20personalized%20healthcare%20advice%20and%20connect%20them%20with%20a%20doctor%20when%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPavelle%20built%20Doctronic%20after%20seeing%20numero