0as%20well.%20Firms%20once%20content%20to%20poach%20young%20talent%20from%20private%20equity's%20ranks%20or%20business%20school%20graduating%20classes%20are%20now%20competing%20with%20banks%20and%20top%20tech%20firms%20for%20undergraduate%20interns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fge0DL%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22hedge%20fund%20employees%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22245%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20career%20of%20big%20trades%20and%20even%20bigger%20paychecks%20might%20seem%20more%20appealing%20than%20ever%2C%20Business%20Insider%20is%20taking%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20work%20at%20an%20elite%20hedge%20fund.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20story%20in%20a%20series%20exploring%20how%20finance%20career%20pathways%20are%20changing%20and%20the%20impact%20on%20young%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20these%20firms%20are%20being%20compared%20against%20investment%20banks%2C%20the%20biggest%20hedge%20funds%20are%20a%20throwback%20to%20a%20time%20when%20Wall%20Street%20pros%20ate%20what%20they%20killed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20went%20hungry%20if%20they%20didn't%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20firms%20can%20be%20quick%20to%20cut%20people%20who%20aren't%20adding%20to%20the%20bottom%20line.%20The%20annual%20churn%20of%20people%20who%20manage%20money%20at%20the%20Big%20Four%20was%20roughly%2020%25%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20alternative%20data%20provider%20Revelio%20Labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20selling%20point%20for%20these%20investing%20conglomerates%20to%20external%20investors%20is%20not%20an%20individual%20money%20manager%20or%20a%20specific%20strategy%20but%20the%20sum%20of%20the%20firm's%20components%2C%20especially%20the%20risk%20management%20systems.%20One%20investor%20in%20hedge%20funds%20described%20these%20firms%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-allocators-due-diligence-multi-strategy-firms-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskill%20factories%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20overcome%20the%20loss%20of%20any%20individual%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChurn%20is%20driven%20by%20firms%20poaching%20rivals'%20star%20performers%20and%20culling%20internal%20underperformers.%20The%20shuffling%20of%20people%20in%20and%20out%20of%20these%20coveted%20seats%20is%20a%20feature%20of%20the%20model%2C%20not%20a%20bug.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20aren't%20places%20to%20build%20a%20career%20usually%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20former%20portfolio%20manager%20who%20has%20worked%20at%20several%20of%20the%20biggest%20multistrategy%20hedge%20fund%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20place%20to%20survive%20and%20get%20paid%20while%20you%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20you%20don't%20know%20when%20things%20will%20turn%20against%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eaab05cd-336c-43bf-9f7e-622e9cb2f9fc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EButterflies%2C%20good%20and%20bad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20play%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bmajors%2C%26quot%3B%20aka%20the%20Big%20Four%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-millennium-point72-balyasny-dominance-changed-the-hedge-fund-industry-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20employ%20roughly%3C%2Fa%3E%20seven%20out%20of%20every%2010%20investment%20professionals%20among%20all%20multistrategy%20hedge%20funds%2C%20you%20need%20plenty%20of%20technical%20and%20interpersonal%20skills%20to%20even%20be%20considered.%20But%20an%20iron%20stomach%20might%20be%20the%20most%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20markets%20turn%20against%20you%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20always%20do%2C%20at%20some%20point%20%E2%80%94%20even%20the%20best%20people%20managing%20money%20get%20%26quot%3Bbutterflies%2C%20and%20not%20the%20good%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20portfolio%20manager%20told%20BI.%20It's%20why%20top%20funds%20employ%20performance%20coaches.%20Zyn%20pouches%20and%20receding%20hairlines%20are%20omnipresent%20on%20hedge%20fund%20trading%20floors%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELosses%20as%20little%20as%205%25%20of%20an%20investment%20portfolio%20in%20a%20week%20can%20result%20in%20a%20pink%20slip%2C%20and%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20biggest%20firms%20gives%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fgraphics%2F2025-hedge-fund-investment-fees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20close%20to%20unlimited%20budget%20to%20recruit%20external%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20replace%20those%20who%20lose%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20losing%20money%20in%20volatility%20events%20is%20a%20really%20important%20part%20of%20investing%20at%20a%20pod%20shop%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brett%20Caughran%2C%20a%20former%20portfolio%20manager%20for%20Citadel%2C%20Schonfeld%2C%20D.E.%20Shaw%2C%20and%20Maverick%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsultants-podcast-inside-look-working-at-citadel-point72-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultistrategy-focused%20training%20firm%20Fundamental%20Edge%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaughran%20tries%20to%20stress%20to%20those%20signing%20up%20for%20his%20training%20that%20working%20at%20a%20multistrategy%20firm%20means%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20a%20moment-by-moment%20paranoia%20about%20the%20systematic%20risks%20in%20my%20portfolio.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20with%20firms%20with%20longer%20investment%20time%20horizons%2C%20where%20he%20said%20people%20could%20ride%20out%20short-term%20volatility%2C%20a%20hypothetical%20Millennium%20portfolio%20manager%20is%20playing%20a%20%26quot%3Bbatting%20average%20game%26quot%3B%20focused%20on%20diversified%2C%20smaller%20bets.%20Concentrated%20firms%2C%20such%20as%20Bill%20Ackman's%20Pershing%20Square%2C%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20few%20home%20runs%2C%20but%20a%20Millennium%20PM%20wants%20to%20hit%20singles%20more%20often%20than%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%20are%20more%20temperamentally%20aligned%20with%20that%2C%20and%20if%20you%20can%20nail%20that%20type%20of%20investing%2C%20there%20are%20great%20rewards%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Billions%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F58b981d5be967327008b484e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20hedge%20fund%20industry%20has%20been%20glamorized%20in%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BBillions.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EShowtime%20%26quot%3BBillions%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESmart%20people%20with%20plenty%20of%20career%20options%20might%20have%20underlying%20motives%20for%20being%20attracted%20to%20such%20a%20high-stress%20environment%2C%20but%20the%20universal%20draw%20is%20the%20paycheck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20proliferation%20of%20portfolio%20managers%20in%20the%20past%20decade%20thanks%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20multistrategy%20hedge%20funds%2C%20these%20jobs%20are%20still%20rare%20and%20come%20with%20serious%20pay%20packages%2C%20such%20as%20a%20bonus%20that%20can%20be%20up%20to%2025%25%20of%20your%20portfolio's%20gains%20for%20yourself%20and%20your%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20make%2020%25%20in%20a%20%241%20billion%20portfolio%20in%20a%20year%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20could%20mean%20a%20%2450%20million%20bonus%20to%20distribute%20between%20your%20small%20team%20of%20analysts%20and%20yourself%2C%20on%20top%20of%20a%20guaranteed%20six-figure%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20mix%20of%20competitiveness%20and%20ego%20that%20drives%20people%20to%20take%20jobs%20at%20the%20biggest%20of%20firms.%20The%20industry%20has%20been%20glamorized%20in%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BBillions%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20loosely%20based%20on%20one%20of%20the%20Big%20Four%20founders%2C%20Point72's%20Steve%20Cohen%2C%20and%20attracts%20type%20A%20personalities%20who%20thrive%20on%20constant%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20multistrategy%20executive%20told%20BI%2C%20when%20the%20calendar%20flips%20to%20a%20new%20year%2C%20%26quot%3Beveryone's%20at%20zero%20again%20%E2%80%94%20and%20no%20one%20cares%20what%20you%20did%20last%20year%2C%20last%20month%2C%20or%20last%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20what-have-you-done-for-me-today-type%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20self-belief%20needed%20to%20play%20in%20the%20majors%2C%20don't%20expect%20any%20self-respecting%20portfolio%20manager%20to%20brag%20about%20a%20good%20run%20around%20the%20office.%20In%20the%20same%20manner%20that%20pitchers%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20no-hitter%20don't%20acknowledge%20it%2C%20PMs%20are%20similarly%20superstitious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20like%20a%20euphoric%20feeling%26quot%3B%20when%20reality%20matches%20with%20your%20research%20and%20strategy%2C%20another%20portfolio%20manager%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20always%20have%20to%20consciously%20suppress%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20person%20said%2C%20and%20stay%20even-keeled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22edc5ad14-dee3-47d7-bfa0-0fd0fd6c85df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20shift%20to%20more%20stable%20teams%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTen%20to%2020%25%20is%20normal%26quot%3B%20churn%20for%20portfolio%20managers%20at%20a%20multimanager%20platform%2C%20said%20Justin%20Young%2C%20director%20of%20investments%20at%20Multilateral%20Endowment%20Management%20Company%2C%20a%20hedge-fund%20investor%20in%20Oklahoma%20that%20manages%20assets%20for%20Oklahoma%20State%20University's%20endowment%20and%20other%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'd%20expect%2015%20to%2020%25%20of%20PMs%20to%20have%20a%20bad%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20industry%20experts%2C%20however%2C%20said%20a%20structural%20shift%20might%20be%20underway%20that%20could%20result%20in%20less%20turnover.%20The%20biggest%20hedge%20funds%20are%20moving%20away%20from%20legions%20of%20PMs%20to%20broader%20teams%20that%20can%20run%20more%20capital%2C%20and%20turnover%20will%20likely%20lessen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebusiness%20development%20executive%20at%20a%20multistrategy%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20tasked%20with%20recruiting%20investing%20talent%20to%20join%20their%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20said%20a%20recent%20industry%20focus%20had%20been%20on%20combining%20investing%20teams%20and%20scaling%20the%20amount%20of%20capital%20the%20combined%20entity%20runs.%20Millennium%2C%20for%20example%2C%20now%20has%20its%20portfolio%20managers%20reporting%20to%20a%20senior%20portfolio%20manager%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fan-inside-look-at-hedge-fund-job-titles-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20often%20oversees%20several%20investors%20in%20larger%20teams%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20money%20in%20the%20portfolio%20and%20the%20higher%20the%20head%20count%2C%20the%20less%20likely%20a%20tough%20quarter%20leads%20to%20a%20cut%2C%20Caughran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTeams%20are%20now%2010%2C%2015%2C%2020%20people%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20not%20cutting%20those%20teams%20when%20they're%20down%202%25%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunds%20might%20be%20pushed%20toward%20such%20a%20strategy%20by%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20talent.%20The%20business%20development%20executive%20said%20young%20finance%20professionals%20working%20in%20banking%20were%20less%20interested%20in%20hedge%20funds%20than%20they%20once%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Yale's%20business%20school%2C%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20investment%20management%20club%20%E2%80%94%20students%20you'd%20think%20would%20be%20ideal%20candidates%20to%20work%20at%20a%20large%20multistrategy%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20are%20more%20interested%20in%20longer-term%20investing%20strategies%20run%20by%20places%20like%20venture%20capital%20firms%20or%20hedge%20funds%20like%20those%20associated%20with%20the%20late%20investor%20Julian%20Robertson%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-tree-shows-how-many-tiger-cub-hedge-funds-there-are-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eknown%20as%20the%20Tiger%20Cubs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Victor%20Ocampo%2C%20the%20club's%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOcampo%20said%20the%20constraints%20of%20working%20at%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20hedge%20funds%20were%20often%20%26quot%3Btoo%20strict%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20given%20their%20demand%20for%20market-beating%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20the%20person%20who%20they're%20going%20to%20fire%20if%20it%20doesn't%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ocampo%2C%20who%20worked%20previously%20as%20a%20portfolio%20manager%20for%20the%20Latin%20American%20investment%20firm%20Sura%20Asset%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20while%20there%20might%20be%20anecdotes%20of%20young%20people%20becoming%20uninterested%20in%20firms%20modeled%20like%20the%20Big%20Four%2C%20the%20data%20show%20that%20these%20funds%20are%20still%20a%20big%20draw.%20Last%20year%2C%20Citadel%20and%20Citadel%20Securities%2C%20the%20market-making%20business%20also%20founded%20by%20Ken%20Griffin%2C%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-summer-internship-ramps-up-recruiting-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%2085%2C000%20applications%20for%20its%20internship%20slots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20more%20than%2030%25%20bump%20from%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIlana%20Weinstein%2C%20a%20longtime%20industry%20recruiter%20who%20runs%20The%20IDW%20Group%2C%20said%20she%20advises%20her%20clients%20to%20ask%20large%20multistrategy%20funds%20what%20percentage%20of%20the%20investing%20team%20is%20homegrown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20firm%20can%20say%20the%20majority%2C%20that%20tells%20you%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20allowing%20for%20some%20footfalls%20and%20giving%20you%20the%20chance%20to%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20all%20multimanagers%20are%20created%20equal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20managers%2C%20Weinstein%20said%2C%20do%20not%20want%20to%20cut%20people%20indiscriminately.%20Point72%2C%20Citadel%2C%20and%20Balyasny%20have%20built%20out%20internship%20and%20training%20programs%20to%20develop%20more%20investing%20and%20technical%20talent%20in-house.%20Millennium%20partners%20with%20UBS%2C%20where%20young%20hires%20spend%20a%20year%20learning%20entry-level%20skills%20at%20the%20investment%20bank%20before%20starting%20at%20the%20hedge%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20firms%20naturally%20have%20a%20vested%20interest%20in%20seeing%20these%20younger%20pros%20grow%20into%20success%20stories%20at%20their%20firms%20instead%20of%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20put%20so%20much%20effort%20into%20recruiting%20talent%20and%20then%20developing%2C%26quot%3B%20Weinstein.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20see%20a%20return%20on%20their%20investment%20and%20give%20these%20people%20time%20to%20adjust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWant%20to%20share%20your%20career%20path%20with%20us%3F%20Fill%20out%20this%20quick%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe9A5QqsX-JIQmtT-1H4IM6UuS5c4Z47_31sWPhjnsqhen8eQ%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Eform%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-hedge-fund-career-multistrategy-portfolio-manager-churn-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published