oftops.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bridge%20the%20gap%2C%20Shani%20connects%20families%20to%20banks.%20%E2%80%9CUp%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20installation%20cost%20can%20be%20financed%20with%20bank%20loans%20at%20an%20interest%20rate%20of%20seven%20to%20eight%20percent.%20That%20means%20families%20only%20have%20to%20pay%2030%20percent%20out%20of%20pocket%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20Rs%2025%2C000%20to%20Rs%2030%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20Pune%2C%20Shilpa%20and%20Suneet%20Kotwal%2C%20founders%20of%20Solum%20Enterprises%2C%20are%20championing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356491%2Fpune-aundh-couple-harness-solar-power-to-run-air-conditioner-ac-bungalow-reduce-electricity-water-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrid-free%20solar%20systems%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20battery%20storage%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20areas%20with%20unstable%20power%20supply.%20%E2%80%9COur%20systems%20cost%20around%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20kilowatt%2C%20but%20include%20batteries%20to%20ensure%20uninterrupted%20usage%2C%E2%80%9D%20Suneet%20explains.%20Although%20costlier%20than%20grid-tied%20systems%2C%20these%20setups%20offer%20independence%20from%20persistent%20outages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20smaller%20operation%2C%20Shilpa%20and%20Suneet%20have%20successfully%20completed%20installations%20for%20various%20clients%2C%20from%20bungalows%20to%20schools.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20keen%20on%20exploring%20grid-free%20community%20solar%20setups%20for%20villages%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shilpa%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E9%20much-needed%20reforms%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20rooftop%20solar%20push%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20four%20founders%20agree%20that%20while%20rooftop%20solar%20installations%20in%20India%20show%20promising%20growth%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20reforms.%20Base