0almost%20like%20a%20huge%20hammock%20that%20finds%20support%20in%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20beams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20walk%20is%20punctuated%20by%20nameplates%20that%20bear%20mention%20of%20the%20different%20species%20of%20birds%20that%20call%20this%20forest%20home%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Hornbill%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebulbuls%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20parakeets.%20The%20walk%20boasts%20pockets%20of%20unprecedented%20stillness%2C%20broken%20only%20by%20the%20sounds%20of%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Came%20here%20as%20a%20boy%20of%2011%20years%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20the%20architect%20who%20built%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20Rahul%20Kadri%3F%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20I%20have%20a%20picture%20with%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoes%20of%20admiration%20follow%20Rahul%20all%20along%20our%20walk.%20He%20is%20something%20of%20a%20celebrity%20on%20the%20walkway.%20But%20even%20as%20the%20city%20applauds%20Rahul%20on%20this%20stroke%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316563%2Ftamil-nadu-sustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20brilliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20particular%20call%20will%20stay%20etched%20in%20his%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20dad%20phoned%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRahul%2C%20what%20have%20you%20done%3F%20Wherever%20I%20go%2C%20they%20talk%20about%20the%20walkway.%20Everybody%20is%20saying%20how%20lovely%20it%20is.%20I%20think%20your%20idea%20was%20excellent.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%2