20walkway%20embodies%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20vision%20for%20nature%20to%20become%20a%20centrepiece%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F419684%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-using-stone-lime-moss-the-timber-residence-vagator%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20architecture%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elevated%20walkway%20begins%20on%20Siri%20Road%20behind%20the%20Kamala%20Nehru%20Park%20and%20ends%20in%20the%20verdant%20sprawl%20of%20the%20Doongerwadi%20Woods.%20Segueing%20into%20the%20conversation%20of%20how%20the%20project%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20Rahul%20backtracks%20to%20one%20of%20his%20walks%20through%20this%20stretch%20during%20the%20COVID-19-induced%20lockdown%2C%20when%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20exploring%20the%20neighbourhood.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20climbed%20over%20the%20fence.%20That%20was%20the%20day%20it%20all%20began%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20What%20followed%20were%20weeks%20of%20%E2%80%9Creading%20the%20site%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20in%20understanding%20how%20the%20site%20works.%20I%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20more%20than%20many%20architects%2C%C2%A0%20imagining%20my%20building.%20I%20love%20to%20be%20on%20the%20site%20alone%20and%20need%20quiet.%20I%20get%20a%20deep%2C%20intuitive%20sense%20of%20how%20things%20need%20to%20unfold.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-2_11zon-1744813850.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Malabar%20Forest%20is%20home%20to%20numerous%20species%20of%20birds%20such